Item 2.02 Results of Operations and Financial Condition.
     On May 6, 2008, Approach Resources Inc. (the "Company") issued a press release announcing the Company's financial and operating results for the three months ended March 31, 2008. The press release contains certain non-GAAP financial information. The reconciliation of such non-GAAP financial information to GAAP financial measures is included in the press release. The press release is furnished herewith as Exhibit 99.1.
Item 7.01 Regulation FD Disclosure.
     The information relating to capital expenditure budget and production guidance for 2008, borrowing base increase and Northern New Mexico contained in the press release attached hereto as Exhibit 99.1 is incorporated herein by reference.
Item 9.01 Financial Statements and Exhibits.
(d)
Exhibits.
