Item 2.02 Results of Operations and Financial Condition.
     On March 2, 2009, Approach Resources Inc. (the "Company") issued a press release announcing its estimated production and reserves for the year ended December 31, 2008. The press release contains certain non-GAAP financial information. The reconciliation of such non-GAAP financial information to GAAP financial measures is included in the press release. A copy of the press release is furnished herewith as Exhibit 99.1.
