     On May 5, 2009, Approach Resources Inc. (the "Company") issued a press release announcing the Company's financial and operating results for the three months ended March 31, 2009. The press release contains certain non-GAAP financial information. The reconciliation of such non-GAAP financial information to GAAP financial measures is included in the press release. The press release is furnished with this current report as Exhibit 99.1.
