     In rendering the opinions expressed below, we have assumed:
 
Approach Resources, Inc. November 11, 2010 Page 2
     (i) The genuineness of all signatures.
     (ii) The authenticity of the originals of the documents submitted to us.
     (iii) The conformity to authentic originals of any documents submitted to us as copies.
     (iv) As to matters of fact, the truthfulness of the representations made or otherwise incorporated in the Underwriting Agreement and representations and statements made in certificates of public officials and officers or other representatives of the Company.
     Based upon the foregoing, and subject to the qualifications and limitations herein set forth, we are of the opinion that the Securities have been duly authorized by all necessary corporate action on the part of the Company and, when sold as described in the Prospectus Supplement, will be validly issued, fully paid and nonassessable.
     Our opinion is limited to Delaware General Corporation Law, including all applicable provisions of the constitution of each such jurisdiction and reported judicial decisions interpreting such laws, and we do not express any opinion herein concerning any other laws.
