 personal property and similar Taxes attributable to the Properties assessed with respect to a period which begins before, and ends after, the Effective Date shall be prorated based on the number of days in such period which fall on each side of the Effective Date (with the day on which the Effective Date falls being counted in the period after the Effective Date); it being expressly understood and agreed by the parties that such ad valorem personal property and similar Taxes will be based on the January 1, 2010 assessed values of the Properties, as reflected in the tax statement billings
