Approach will host a conference call on Friday, March 9, 2012, at 10:00 a.m. Central Time (11:00 a.m. Eastern Time) to discuss fourth quarter and full year 2011 financial and operating results. The conference call can be accessed by dialing (800) 510-9661 (U.S. domestic) or (617) 614-3452 (International). Additionally, the conference call will be broadcast live over the internet and can be accessed through the Investor Relations section of the Company's website, . The webcast will be archived for replay on the Company's website until June 6, 2012.
