10
 
Misconception vs. Facts
Misconception: Wells are gassier as the play moves southward
Gassier wells are historical Canyon, Strawn and Ellenburger wells
The Wolfcamp Shale is located in peak oil and early wet gas window. Wolfcamp wells are expected to produce more than 50% oil and ~80% liquids over the production life, supported by core data, initial production data and EUR forecast
