(3) Initially, U.S. Bank National Association, the Trustee under the Indenture, will act as Paying Agent and Security Registrar. The Company may change any Paying Agent or Security Registrar without notice to any Holder. The Company may act in any such capacity.
PAYING AGENT AND SECURITY REGISTRAR.
